feed.title: Pallisters Reserve Orford
feed.subtitle: Pallisters Reserve is a Trust for Nature owned property near Orford and is managed by the Friends of Pallisters Reserve. The property is open on the 4th Sunday each month and visitors are welcome to attend. Contact Leader, Peter Carrucan at pjcarrucan@lakegnotuk.com.au for more information Web: www.warrnambool.org/pallisters
